headline: Analysts Turn Bullish on Xcel Energy (XEL) Amid Data Center Boom
summary: Xcel Energy Inc. (NASDAQ:XEL) is one of the best infrastructure stocks to buy right now. On February 13, UBS upgraded Xcel Energy Inc.
